  Locus:
    Page: 253
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Humility
---
Do not consider yourself to have made any spiritual progress, unless
you account yourself the least of all men. ... Resolve to do the will of
others rather than your own. Always choose to possess less rather than
more. Always take the lowest plane, and regard yourself as less than others.
